[
    {
        "content": "<p>How can I create a data type that contains both a SpinLock and a data type whose creation can fail?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Inner</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">u32</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">u32</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Other</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Other</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">new</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Result</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nb\">Ok</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">{})</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"cp\">#[pin_data]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">u32</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"cp\">#[pin]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">d</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">SpinLock</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Inner</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">o</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Other</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">new</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">try_pin_init</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">10</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">d</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">new_spinlock</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Inner</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">20</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">30</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">}),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">o</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Other</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">new</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">})</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><code>new_spinlock!</code> seems to be only usable with <code>pin_init</code>, but Other needs try_pin_init, so…</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">error</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">E0277</span><span class=\"p\">]:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">trait</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">bound</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">pin_init</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Example</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">error</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Error</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">pin_init</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Example</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">not</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">satisfied</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">drm</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">jq</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">42</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">17</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"o\">|</span>\n<span class=\"mi\">42</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">new</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\">                 </span><span class=\"o\">^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">trait</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">pin_init</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Example</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">not</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">implemented</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">pin_init</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Example</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">error</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Error</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"err\">`</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"o\">|</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">help</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">following</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">other</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">types</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">implement</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">trait</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">pin_init</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">AlwaysFail</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">implements</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">pin_init</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"err\">`</span>\n<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">ChainInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">I</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">implements</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">pin_init</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"err\">`</span>\n<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">ChainPinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">I</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">implements</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">pin_init</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"err\">`</span>\n<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">core</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">result</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nb\">Result</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">implements</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">pin_init</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">PinInit</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"err\">`</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 555531263,
        "sender_full_name": "Philipp Stanner",
        "timestamp": 1763109700
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Or is it that the return type needs to be a PinInit error version?</p>",
        "id": 555531789,
        "sender_full_name": "Philipp Stanner",
        "timestamp": 1763109899
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>When you write <code>impl PinInit&lt;T&gt;</code> then you are saying that the initializer is infallible. Change the return type to <code>impl PinInit&lt;T, Error&gt;</code>.</p>",
        "id": 555537336,
        "sender_full_name": "Alice Ryhl",
        "timestamp": 1763111497
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Ah yes, thx…</p>\n<p>And how would I canonically properly create something like  <code>Arc&lt;Revocable&lt;SpinLock&lt;Inner&gt;&gt;&gt;</code>?</p>\n<p>Ultimately I have</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Inner</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Outer</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">inner</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Arc</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Revocable</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">SpinLock</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Inner</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Outer</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">new</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Result</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Do I have to describe every stage with pin, and then only the creator of Outer actually allocates everything?</p>",
        "id": 555538488,
        "sender_full_name": "Philipp Stanner",
        "timestamp": 1763111832
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I think you would write:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">inner</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Arc</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">pin_init</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Revocable</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">new</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">new_spinlock</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Inner</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">new</span><span class=\"p\">())))</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>with <code>Inner::new()</code> being a method that returns <code>impl PinInit&lt;Inner, _&gt;</code></p>",
        "id": 555539305,
        "sender_full_name": "Alice Ryhl",
        "timestamp": 1763112076
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>But could I then construct <code>Outer::new() -&gt; Result&lt;KBox&lt;Self&gt;&gt;</code> or would I end up with having to return a <code>PinInit&lt;Self, Error&gt;</code>, too?</p>",
        "id": 555541723,
        "sender_full_name": "Philipp Stanner",
        "timestamp": 1763112840
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><code>Outer::new() </code> can return a <code>Result&lt;Self&gt;</code> or <code>Result&lt;KBox&lt;Self&gt;&gt;</code> or whatever you want.</p>",
        "id": 555542288,
        "sender_full_name": "Alice Ryhl",
        "timestamp": 1763113024
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>The <code>Arc::pin_init</code> call runs the initializer, so you are not forced to return an initializer to the caller.</p>",
        "id": 555542330,
        "sender_full_name": "Alice Ryhl",
        "timestamp": 1763113038
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"692273\">Philipp Stanner</span> has marked this topic as resolved.</p>",
        "id": 555575057,
        "sender_full_name": "Notification Bot",
        "timestamp": 1763123120
    }
